I'm following the dev certificate course. One of the things I have to do is creating a template.
I have to use {% module_block %} but I get and interpret error about a widget tag

I have the following code and it won't publish
```{% module_block "my_rich_text_module" path="@HubSpot/rich_text.module" label="My Rich Text Field Module" %}
